* read/write settings from/to the ini-file
* show a size of the font when drawing it
* ability to type any text when displaying the font
* customization support:
	* colors (directory listing, font drawing)
	* window resize + fullscreen support
	* keyboard shortcuts
	* a gamepad support
	* font & its size for UI (dir. listing, fileinfo)
* fast changing of the selected file via PgUp/PgDown keys
